description: Jellyfish dongers are similar to the squid ones except they look more round and squishy. Use a ( , @ , or a capital letter C to get that rounded head look. They’re pretty cute. It is common for many jellyfish to swim together, so you may as well go ahead and make a whole bunch of them together. （：。）ミ Ｃ：。ミ Ｃ：｡ミ @:≈
title: Jellyfish
